OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779437195
OL,3,CTeacher 'ashamed' but denies murder
OL,4,Cand abuse of baby, court hears
OL,6,FA teacher accused of the murder of an
OL,7,Fadopted baby told a jury he never hurt
OL,8,For sexually abused the child.
OL,10,FJamie Varley, 37, became emotional at
OL,11,Ftimes during his evidence from the
OL,12,Fwitness box as he denied the murder of
OL,13,F13-month-old Preston Davey.
OL,15,FHe denied taking photos or videos as
OL,16,F"trophies" of sexual abuse but said he
OL,17,Ffelt "disappointed" and "really
OL,18,Fashamed" at some images he had taken
OL,19,Fon his phone.
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@JO]yD@FOUyD@SO]yD@YOUzD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/17
