FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779437195
OL,3,CTeacher 'ashamed' but denies murder
OL,4,Cand abuse of baby, court hears
OL,6,FVarley is alleged to have routinely
OL,7,Fsexually, physically and emotionally
OL,8,Fabused the baby he had adopted with
OL,9,Fhis partner John McGowan-Fazakerley,
OL,10,F32, Preston Crown Court has heard.
OL,12,FBoth men deny all charges.
OL,14,FIn the fourth week of the trial Varley
OL,15,Fgave evidence in his own defence for
OL,16,Fthe first time, his voice sometimes
OL,17,Fbreaking with emotion as videos and
OL,18,Fphotos of the baby were shown on
OL,19,Fscreens in the courtroom.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
