PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779437195
OL,3,CTeacher 'ashamed' but denies murder
OL,4,Cand abuse of baby, court hears
OL,6,FNick Johnson KC, defending Varley,
OL,7,Fbegan his questions by asking him: "On
OL,8,Fthe 27th of July 2023, did you kill
OL,9,FPreston Davey by deliberately blocking
OL,10,Fhis airway?
OL,12,F"No, I did not," Varley replied.
OL,14,FMr Johnson continued: "Did you
OL,15,Fsexually assault that child in any way?
OL,17,F"Did you ever wilfully harm Preston
OL,18,Fphysically or psychologically?"
OL,26,@oD@dOUtD@AOUtD@PO]vD@WOUyD@AOUzD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/17
