OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779437195
OL,3,CTeacher 'ashamed' but denies murder
OL,4,Cand abuse of baby, court hears
OL,6,FVarley replied: "Absolutely not, our
OL,7,Fson has never been sexually abused.
OL,8,FNo."
OL,10,FJurors heard, after undergoing an
OL,11,Fassessment and familiarisation
OL,12,Fprocess, Preston was adopted and began
OL,13,Fliving with the defendants at their
OL,14,Fhome in Blackpool on 1 April 2023.
OL,26,@nD@QOUpD@DO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
