PN,39405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779437195
OL,3,CTeacher 'ashamed' but denies murder
OL,4,Cand abuse of baby, court hears
OL,6,FBut it is alleged in the next four
OL,7,Fmonths before his death he was
OL,8,Froutinely ill-treated, had indecent
OL,9,Fimages and videos taken of him, and
OL,10,Fwas sexually abused and physically
OL,11,Fassaulted, suffering 40 traumatic
OL,12,Finjuries found at post mortem.
OL,14,FThe court heard Varley, who said he
OL,15,Fhas severe dyslexia, became a design
OL,16,Fand technology teacher and head of
OL,17,Fyear at a local high school before
OL,18,Fmeeting his partner.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
