PN,39406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779437195
OL,3,CTeacher 'ashamed' but denies murder
OL,4,Cand abuse of baby, court hears
OL,6,FHe said: "I had always thought about
OL,7,Fhaving kids, I wanted to be a teacher,
OL,8,Fa daddy, just never thought it was
OL,9,Fpossible once I realised I was a gay
OL,10,Fman.
OL,12,F"John was everything I had ever asked
OL,13,Ffor in a relationship.
OL,15,F"My whole life just changed when I met
OL,16,FJohn."
OL,18,FVarley said the "early stages" of
OL,19,Fadoption was an "eye opener" and that
OL,20,FPreston was not a good sleeper or in a
OL,21,Froutine.
OL,26,@nD@JOUtD@AOUwD@AOUxD@FO]zD@QOUzD@^O]{D@
OL,26,AQOU{D@\O]
