OL,3,CTeacher 'ashamed' but denies murder
OL,4,Cand abuse of baby, court hears
OL,6,FHe added: "It was challenging in the
OL,7,Fsense it was new to us.
OL,9,F"I felt because I had more experience
OL,10,Fthan John, I felt it was going to be a
OL,11,Fbreeze, but it wasn't."
OL,13,FValret was asked to explain a text he
OL,14,Fsent to his sister about Preston,
OL,15,Fsaying: "He's dead meat" after a
OL,16,Fsleepless night.
OL,18,FVarley said: "It was just language
OL,19,Fthat I use. In social settings I'm
OL,20,Fdramatic. Sassy. I just easily throw
OL,21,Fwords about."
OL,26,@nD@KOUqD@AOUsD@WO]wD@IOUwD@XO]zD@NOU}D@
