OL,3,CTeacher 'ashamed' but denies murder
OL,4,Cand abuse of baby, court hears
OL,6,FThe defendant told jurors he had
OL,7,Fbonded with the baby better than he
OL,8,Fexpected, as he did not think he could
OL,9,Flove anything more than his dog, Max,
OL,10,Fbut his love for Preston exceeded that
OL,11,Ffor his pet.
OL,13,FHe added: "When we got the little one,
OL,14,Fit was special, it was quick, it was
OL,15,Fstrong."
OL,26,@uD@KOUwD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/17
