PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779437195
OL,3,CTeacher 'ashamed' but denies murder
OL,4,Cand abuse of baby, court hears
OL,6,FMr Johnson then asked Varley about
OL,7,Fphotos of bruises on Preston, who
OL,8,Fappeared to have a "cluster" of
OL,9,Fbruises on his forehead, which child
OL,10,Fsex abuse expert, Dr Joanne Gifford,
OL,11,Fhad described as a "red flag" for
OL,12,Fsigns of abuse.
OL,14,FVarley said the baby, who was learning
OL,15,Fto crawl, would often bang his head
OL,16,Fand daily have little mishaps but
OL,17,Fdenied ever deliberately bruising the
OL,18,Fchild.
OL,26,@pD@TOUpD@\O]sD@TOUsD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/17
