PN,39410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779437195
OL,3,CTeacher 'ashamed' but denies murder
OL,4,Cand abuse of baby, court hears
OL,6,FMr Johnson asked about a photo of
OL,7,FPreston playing naked in a paddling
OL,8,Fpool which Home Office pathologist Dr
OL,9,FAlison Armour said showed a shaded
OL,10,Fmark on the child's bottom which
OL,11,Fresembled a human bite mark.
OL,13,FMr Johnson said: "Did you ever bite
OL,14,FPreston's bottom?
OL,16,F"What do you say to the suggestion you
OL,17,Fbit him and took a photo?"
OL,19,FVarley replied: "Absolutely not.
OL,21,F"Could not be more wrong."
OL,26,@uD@ROUxD@AOUyD@ZO]{D@QOU}D@AOU}D@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/17
