PN,39411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779437195
OL,3,CTeacher 'ashamed' but denies murder
OL,4,Cand abuse of baby, court hears
OL,6,FMr Johnson asked Varley about a series
OL,7,Fof photos on Varley's phone of Preston
OL,8,Fin his cot, along with two toy teddy
OL,9,Fbears, four days before his death in
OL,10,FJuly 2023.
OL,12,FThe images stretch over a period of
OL,13,Fthree minutes and 12 seconds, with the
OL,14,Fchild's head and arms over the top
OL,15,Fhorizontal bar of his cot and his neck
OL,16,Fresting on the bar.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
