FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779437195
OL,3,CTeacher 'ashamed' but denies murder
OL,4,Cand abuse of baby, court hears
OL,6,FHis body is apparently partially
OL,7,Fsuspended, his legs in a "frog like"
OL,8,Fposition and the child seemingly
OL,9,Fasleep or unconscious, described to
OL,10,Fthe jury earlier as a "very unsafe"
OL,11,Fand "dangerous" position.
OL,13,FVarley said the baby had gone to sleep
OL,14,Fbefore in "funny positions" and had
OL,15,Fdone so again so he took photos.
OL,17,FMr Johnson said: "Were these trophies
OL,18,Fof a sexual encounter?"
OL,20,F"No they were not, no," Varley replied.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUoD@dO]rD@WOUrD@cO]sD@EOUsD@OO]vD@
OL,26,AKOUvD@[O]yD@ROUzD@WO]|D@AOU|D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/17
