SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779437195
OL,3,CTeacher 'ashamed' but denies murder
OL,4,Cand abuse of baby, court hears
OL,6,FHe added: "I did not even recognise at
OL,7,Fthe moment, it was inappropriate.
OL,9,F"I'm disappointed. I feel shamed. I
OL,10,Ffeel really ashamed.
OL,12,F"I did not mean to cause any distress,
OL,13,Fany harm in that moment, I felt he was
OL,14,Fsafe.
OL,16,F"I just wanted to capture him, all of
OL,17,Fhis life.
OL,19,F"I just wanted to capture every part
OL,20,Fof his life."
OL,26,@nD@KOUqD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOU{D@AOU|D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/17
