PN,39414
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779437195
OL,3,CTeacher 'ashamed' but denies murder
OL,4,Cand abuse of baby, court hears
OL,6,FFour days later Preston was rushed to
OL,7,Fhospital on 27 July 2023, having
OL,8,Fsuffered a collapse and cardiac
OL,9,Farrest, allegedly following a sexual
OL,10,Fassault by Varley.
OL,12,FVarley told police he had briefly left
OL,13,Fthe child in the bath and when he
OL,14,Freturned he was off his bath seat and
OL,15,Fsubmerged.
OL,17,FBut a post-mortem examination ruled
OL,18,Fout drowning and found multiple non-
OL,19,Faccidental, internal and external
OL,20,Finjuries.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
