PN,39415
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779437195
OL,3,CTeacher 'ashamed' but denies murder
OL,4,Cand abuse of baby, court hears
OL,6,FPreston's cause of death was found to
OL,7,Fbe acute upper airways obstruction by
OL,8,Feither smothering or an object or
OL,9,Fobjects inserted into his mouth.
OL,11,FThe jury has heard some injuries to
OL,12,FPreston were possibly caused by
OL,13,F"forcible penetration" and parts of
OL,14,Fhis anatomy "abnormal" with his
OL,15,Finjuries clinical signs of sexual
OL,16,Fabuse.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@VO]vD@MOUvD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/17
